data.description: Welcome to this beautiful farmhouse-style home in Riverview Plantation! With its 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths, this home offers plenty of space for comfortable living. The open floor plan adds a sense of spaciousness and allows for a seamless flow between rooms. It's great to hear that the home has undergone abundance of recent updates, some of them are including brand new carpet, laminate wood flooring, paint inside and outside, kitchen cabinets , black stainless-steel appliances, and granite countertops. These upgrades not only enhance the aesthetic appeal but also provide a fresh and modern feel to the interior. The quiet and peaceful atmosphere in Riverview Plantation is an attractive feature that adds to the overall appeal of the neighborhood. It allows residents to enjoy a serene and relaxing environment, making it a perfect place to unwind and enjoy the surroundings.
